{"id":1098,"name":"Letter from Lipsius, Justus to Clusius, Carolus, 1602-08-08","paralleltexts":{"Diplomatic":{"text":"<body>I[ustus] Lipsius Carolo Clusio S[alutem] D[icit].\n Si vales, optime Clusi, ex animo gaudeo; ego medie, id est male; et tamen pugnare etiam libuit, an potius <ab id=\"9027200\"/>repugnare<ae id=\"9027200\"/>? Hic videbis; nos <ab id=\"9027201\"/>tua reliqua<ae id=\"9027201\"/> quando? Impone <ab id=\"9027202\"/>summam manum<ae id=\"9027202\"/> ante summum illum diem, qui ut tardus tibi veniat Deum precor.\n Lovanii, VI. Idus Sextil[es] M.DCII.\n  \n    [<i>Address</i>:] V[iro] C[larissimo] Carolo Clusio.\n    [<i>Clusii manu</i>:] 1602. Lipsii. Lovanii, VI Id[us] Sextiles. Accepi Leydae VI Kal[endas] Sept[embres].  Respondi XVI Kal[endas] Octob[res]</body>","annotations":[{"text":"tua reliqua: The sequel to the <span><em>Rariorum plantarum historia</em>, the <em>Exoticorum libri decem</em>,  printed by Franciscus Raphelengius Jr in Leiden, in 1605 </span>","n":9027201,"type":{"description":"Any annotation","name":"Uncategorized"}},{"text":"summam manum: Cf. Erasmus, <em>Adagia</em>, 1, 2, 34.","n":9027202,"type":{"description":"Any annotation","name":"Uncategorized"}},{"text":"repugnare: An allusion to Lipsius&apos;s most recent work, <br/><span> the <em></em></span><span><em>Dispunctio notarum </em>(Antwerp: J. Moretus, 1602)</span><span><em></em>, a fierce reaction against an anonymous humanist who had attacked Lipsius&apos;s edition of Tacitus. Lipsius probably also sent a copy of the <em>De bibliothecis</em>, since both works were issued at the same time.</span>","n":9027200,"type":{"description":"Any annotation","name":"Uncategorized"}}]}},"facsimiles":[{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893589_CLUY020-017-a.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-huygens-viewer-2.0/viewer.html?rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893589_CLUY020-017-a.jp2"},{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893590_CLUY020-017-b.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-huygens-viewer-2.0/viewer.html?rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/893590_CLUY020-017-b.jp2"},{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/CLUY020-017-a.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-huygens-viewer-2.0/viewer.html?rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/CLUY020-017-a.jp2"},{"thumbnail":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-djatoka/resolver?url_ver=Z39.88-2004&svc_id=info:lanl-repo/svc/getRegion&svc_val_fmt=info:ofi/fmt:kev:mtx:jpeg2000&svc.format=image/jpeg&svc.level=0&rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/CLUY020-017-b.jp2","zoom":"https://tomcat.tiler01.huygens.knaw.nl/adore-huygens-viewer-2.0/viewer.html?rft_id=http://localhost:8080/jp2/clusius/CLUY020-017-b.jp2"}],"metadata":[{"field":"Letter code","value":"CLUY020-017"},{"field":"Sender","value":"Lipsius, Justus"},{"field":"Place of creation","value":"Leuven"},{"field":"Recipient","value":"Clusius, Carolus"},{"field":"Place of receipt","value":"Leiden"},{"field":"Date","value":"1602-08-08"},{"field":"Language","value":"Latin"},{"field":"Signature","value":"o: University Library Leiden, ms. Vulc. 101 (L); cl: ibid., ms. Lips. 3(4), f. 167."},{"field":"Source of transcription/edition","value":"ILE XV, 02 08 08 L"},{"field":"Source of translation","value":""},{"field":"Notes","value":""},{"field":"Editor","value":